{"tid":2451531,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曾製作4Minute、BEAST的洪勝成會長將推出新女團HOT ISSUE！4月正式出道成熱話","createTime":"2021-03-18T07:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T15:16:18.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3dfddceea3ae2ad0db0184a13a50e83f2c8c1b16","tid":2451531,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/g96875IU_mM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fg96875IU_mM&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=90ac4d28\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/g96875IU_mM</a><br />\n<br />\n據報導，曾製作4Minute、BEAST等人氣組合的洪勝成會長帶領的S2娛樂將推出新人女子組合，吸引了大眾的視線。"},{"pid":"780aad797f3846bc5bee891fba67d1bc18632c08","tid":2451531,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"S2娛樂於官方SNS公開了新人女子組合HOT ISSUE的官方標誌影片，並發佈了組合即將出道的消息。在公開的影片中，讓人聯想起H和S的圖像元素被製作成標誌。另外，兩邊的標點符號似乎相互連接的樣子，表現了大衆和HOT ISSUE連接在一起的意思。<br />\n<br />\n在公開標誌影像的前一天，組合開通了官方SNS，並公開了組合名稱，以及預告了下個月正式出道的消息，讓大眾對新組合的期待也越來越高。"},{"pid":"0b6a1ff70aa47b65017b40a6e45ef86f2cfacbca","tid":2451531,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDZBwQU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDZBwQU.png&h=39101b24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n組合名「HOT ISSUE」的HOT是Honest、Outstanding、Terrific的縮寫，表達了要在歌謠界製造坦率、優秀話題的雄心壯志。"},{"pid":"a4a1b82e0172c255f0576fe2ea31d81a52caae38","tid":2451531,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYjt7pq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYjt7pq.png&h=d9c4ca34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n引領S2娛樂的洪勝成會長曾擔任JYP娛樂公司的代表，2008年創立了CUBE娛樂，是培養了4Minute、BEAST、BTOB、CLC、PENTAGON、(G)I-DLE等著名偶像組合的製作人，因此，本次HOT ISSUE的出道更加令人期待。"},{"pid":"9b64b4d2377b8b5386b8e0bb542134350ee00731","tid":2451531,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:28:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HOTISSUE_S2/status/1372110466059735053?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHOTISSUE_S2%2Fstatus%2F1372110466059735053%3Fs%3D20&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2bXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=4d90e5bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHOTISSUE_S2%2Fstatus%2F1372110466059735053%3Fs%3D20&h=edf8ec62\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HOTISSUE_S2/status/1372110466059735053?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"941ee8ed9337c051925381d5c8edf27ef55d26c9","tid":2451531,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rw8uRUo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frw8uRUo.png&h=f51aefe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nS2娛樂表示：「HOT ISSUE以4月正式出道歌謠界爲目標，正在加緊準備中。希望大家多多關注引領K-POP全球化的，具有獨特魅力的HOT ISSUE。」"},{"pid":"30da6d69e0fcde36b2a29907db174679f09ff3a5","tid":2451531,"uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"個名係咪用4m首歌名改 回憶下先 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"947d0acadbe2287543c53afc3c25b1b88f9d7f5c","tid":2451531,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會係另一隊好似TRIBE咁既團 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/16/092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F16%2F092405_56a374376ca6836dc9daf28eb270f8f2.gif&h=ca67a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fcfd5f4c958a0e2c8357b620acc4f85bfe34531","tid":245153